        "zh": "1.臨床試驗簡介<br>2.臨床試驗之倫理議題<br>3.研究程序與抽樣<br>4.資料的整理<br>5.敘述統計<br>6.推論統計<br>",
        "en": "1. Introduction to clinical trials<br>2. Ethical issues in clinical trials<br>3. Research procedure and sampling<br>4.Data presentation<br>5.Descriptive statistics<br>6. Inference statistics<br>"
